API:
1. Auth(user, pass, deviceId) return token
2. Register(user, pass, deviceId, email, name) return bool
3. Sync(user, token, deviceId, jsonData) return bool
jsonData: deviceTime, timezone, heartRate, bodyTemperature, GPSLocation, batteryLevel, stressLevel, inActiveDuration
4. Push(groupId, userId, deviceId, pushTime, message) return bool


